# Soy garlic fried chicken sauce

Combine all ingredients for in a small saucepan. Bring it to a boil over medium high heat, keep boiling for 3 to 5 minutes. Stir occasionally.

- soy sauce | 1/4 cup | 
- mirin | 1/2 cup | 
- sugar | 1/4 cup | 
- garlic | 5 cloves chopped | 
- Thai chili flakes chili | 2 to 3 tbsp or 5 to 10 whole dried | 
